1: Requirement Analysis
👤 User Features
Register / Login
Upload PDF book
View PDF online
Download PDF
Search books
See list of uploaded books

👨‍💼 Admin Features
Delete inappropriate books
Manage users

2: Tech Stack
Frontend → HTML/CSS/JS (or React)
Backend → Node.js + Express.js
Database → MongoDB
File Upload → Multer (middleware)


3: Database Design
🗄 Users Collection
User
- _id
- name
- email
- password (hashed)
- role (user/admin)
📚 Books Collection
Book
- _id
- title
- author
- description
- pdfFilePath
- uploadedBy (userId)
- uploadDate




